__NOTOC__
[[Mr. Store]] is a high-class store in [[Market Square]]. Mr. Shopkeeper doesn't deal in such piffling currency as Meat; instead, shoppers trade in [[Mr. Accessory|Mr. Accessories]] to buy things.  In addition to the regular offerings, there is a Special of the Month which changes monthly.

